fields.title: Senior System Engineer
fields.description: We are seeking a highly skilled Senior System Engineer to join our dynamic IT team. The ideal candidate will design, implement, maintain, and optimize our IT infrastructure to ensure optimal performance, security, and reliability. You will be expected to collaborate across teams to deliver innovative solutions, support critical business processes, and uphold the highest standards of system performance and reliability.
fields.requirements:
Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related field.

Minimum of 5 years of experience in system engineering roles.

Demonstrated experience with virtualization technologies (VMware, Hyper-V).

Solid experience managing Linux and Windows server environments.

Familiarity with cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud).

Strong understanding of networking fundamentals and security practices.
fields.responsibilities:
Design, deploy, and manage complex IT systems and infrastructures, ensuring high availability and scalability.

Monitor system performance, security, and reliability; proactively address issues to maintain operational continuity.

Develop and implement infrastructure improvements and enhancements.

Collaborate with cross-functional teams to analyze business requirements and deliver technical solutions.

Provide expert-level troubleshooting, diagnostics, and resolution of complex system issues.

Ensure compliance with IT security policies, standards, and procedures.

Document system configurations, processes, and procedures clearly and accurately.
